    "gp_shopify_original_section_624186990916535030": {
      "type": "gp-section-624186990916535030",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "",
        "ggq2iXQSQ3p_text": "FAQs",
        "ggx2MigoWNo_text": "<p>Got questions? We’ve got answer...</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_0": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_1": "<p>Who is Gemix suitable for?</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_2": "<p>How many capsules should I take per day?</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_3": "<p>What makes Gemix different from other hair supplements?</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_4": "<p>Is it suitable for vegans or vegetarians?</p>",
        "ggmgxcjsL4s_childItem_5": "<p>Is there a money-back guarantee?</p>",
        "ggVJoohCSzA_text": "<p>Most users begin to notice reduced shedding and stronger hair within 4–6 weeks. Fuller growth is typically seen after 8–12 weeks of consistent use.</p>",
        "ggBxVTyAVRH_text": "<p>Follix is designed for adults of all genders experiencing hair thinning, shedding, or slow growth. It’s safe for most people, but check with your doctor if you’re pregnant, nursing, or have a medical condition.</p>",
        "ggf3POMIrCX_text": "<p>Only 2 capsules a day for real results. Take it with water, preferably after a meal.</p>",
        "ggy9YeAXGOh_text": "<p>It combines marine collagen, salmon cartilage extract, biotin, and other clinically studied ingredients in one powerful capsule—no fillers, no fluff, just real results.</p>",
        "ggrLtAUQIVy_text": "<p>No. Follix contains marine collagen and salmon cartilage, so it is not vegan or vegetarian.</p>",
        "ggqJL6ePOfg_text": "<p>Yes! We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you’re not happy with your results, contact us for a refund.</p>"
      }
    },
